  "text": "This paper is based on earlier work [CITATION_1] , which has been revised and extended. CONOISE-G is funded by the DTI and EPSRC through the Welsh e-Science Centre, in collaboration with the Research and Venture division of BT Group CTO. The research in this paper is also funded in part by the EPSRC Mohican Project (Reference no: GR/R32697/01).",
